m, the earth trembled, and the heavens dropped, the clouds also dropped water."},{"id":"recqSwYRohtXZxW5r","ref":"Judg.5.5","text":"The mountains melted from before the LORD, even that Sinai from before the LORD God of Israel."},{"id":"recxZQwhw0npAEKNz","ref":"Judg.5.6","text":"In the days of Shamgar the son of Anath, in the days of Jael, the highways were unoccupied, and the travellers walked through byways."},{"id":"reci9pGT3KR1KaJ8B","ref":"Judg.5.7","text":"The inhabitants of the villages ceased, they ceased in Israel, until that I Deborah arose, that I arose a mother in Israel."},{"id":"recItcZ4OZZH2keNu","ref":"Judg.5.8","text":"They chose new gods; then was war in the gates: was there a shield or spear seen among forty thousand in Israel?"}]}
